sudo vi /boot/cmdline.txt

Then add $usbhid.mousepoll=0 into one of the line. Example as follow:
dwc_otg.lpm_enable=0 console=serial0,115200 console=tty1 root=/dev/mmcblk0p2 rootfstype=ext4 elevator=deadline fsck.repair=yes rootwait ipv6.disable=1 usbhid.mousepoll=0 quiet splash plymouth.ignore-serial-consoles

sudo reboot

Visit this link : https://forums.raspberrypi.com/viewtopic.php?t=188705
